Seton于1438年11月出生在苏格兰哈丁頓史爾西頓时，他的父亲George Seton24岁，母亲Margaret Stewart32岁。他于1459年1月20日与Christian Lindsay在苏格兰结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1474年7月19日在他的家乡享年35岁，埋葬在英国苏格兰哈丁頓史爾西頓。"},"hr":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"studeni 1438.–19. srpnja 1474.","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449.–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451.","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20. siječnja 1459.","8 Jan 1461":"8. siječnja 1461.","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19. srpnja 1474.","1476":"1476.","Nov 1438":"studeni 1438.","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449.","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"listopad 1438–19. července 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20. ledna 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8. ledna 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19. července 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"listopad 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Skotsko, United Kingdom"},"da":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"november 1438–19. juli 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20. januar 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8. januar 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19. juli 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"november 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Skotland","Scotland":"Skotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Skotland, United Kingdom"},"nl":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"november 1438–19 juli 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20 januari 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8 januari 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19 juli 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"november 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Schotland","Scotland":"Schotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Schotland, Verenigd Koninkrijk"},"en":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"November 1438–19 July 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20 January 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8 January 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19 July 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"November 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Seton","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Scottish (Midlothian) and English: variant of   Seaton  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Seaton","meanings":["English: habitational name from any of various places called Seaton, such as those in Cumberland, Devon, Durham, Leicestershire, Northumberland, Rutland, East Yorkshire, and North Yorkshire, most of which derive from Old English <i>sǣ</i> ‘sea, lake’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, estate’, though the Leicestershire placename probably arises from an Old English personal name <i>Sǣga</i> or a stream-name <i>Sǣge</i> (from Old English <i>sǣge</i> ‘slow moving’; compare   Seabrook  ) + Old English <i>tūn</i>.","Scottish: habitational name from Seton (East Lothian), from Old English <i>sǣ</i> ‘sea’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, estate’."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Contracted form of Old French <i>Jo(h)anne</i>, from Latin <i>Io(h)anna</i> (  see  Joanna  ). In England this was the usual feminine form of   John   from the Middle English period onwards and was extremely popular, but in the 16th and 17th centuries it steadily lost ground to   Jane .  It was strongly revived in the first part of the 20th century, partly under the influence of  George Bernard Shaw's  play St Joan (  1923 ), based on the life of  Joan of Arc  (  1412–31 ). Claiming to be guided by the voices of the saints, she persuaded the French dauphin to defy the occupying English forces and have himself crowned, and she led the French army that raised the siege of Orleans in  1429 . The following year she was captured by the Burgundians and sold to the English, and a year later she was burned at the stake for witchcraft at the age of 18 or 19. Her story has captured the imagination of many writers, and she is variously portrayed as a national and political hero, a model of apolitical straightforwardness and honesty, and a religious heroine. She was canonized in  1920 . More recent influences have included the American film actress  Joan Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When John Seton was born in November 1438, in Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland, his father, George Seton, was 24 and his mother, Margaret Stewart, was 32. He married Christian Lindsay on 20 January 1459, in Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died on 19 July 1474, in his hometown, at the age of 35, and was buried in Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland, United Kingdom."},"et":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"november 1438–19. juuli 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20. jaanuar 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8. jaanuar 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19. juuli 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"november 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"marraskuu 1438–19. heinäkuuta 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20. tammikuuta 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8. tammikuuta 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19. heinäkuuta 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"marraskuu 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406","1449":"1449","1438":"1438","Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Seton, East Lothian, Scotland":"Seton, Haddingtonshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Nov 1438–19 Jul 1474":"novembre 1438–19 juillet 1474","1438–1474":"1438–1474","1435–1496":"1435–1496","1449–1508":"1449–1508","1415–1478":"1415–1478","1406–1461":"1406–1461","1451":"1451","1461":"1461","20 January 1459":"20 janvier 1459","8 Jan 1461":"8 janvier 1461","1415":"1415","1435":"1435","1478":"1478","19 Jul 1474":"19 juillet 1474","1476":"1476","Nov 1438":"novembre 1438","1496":"1496","1474":"1474","1508":"1508","1406":"1406",